[SN]TITLE[SN]
Boy, 13, arrested over Swansea indecent assaults

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A 13-year-old boy has been arrested following a number of indecent assaults in Swansea city centre.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Four incidents have been reported in an area near the civic centre and the Marriott hotel in the afternoons between 4 July and 7 July.
Officers said lone women were approached and were touched inappropriately.
South Wales Police said a boy is being held at Swansea central police station.
